OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine in
OL,7,Fplaces. Then mostly dry overnight,
OL,8,Fperhaps the odd light shower across
OL,9,FMoray. Freshening westerly breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA dry and warm day with some
OL,12,Fhazy sunshine developing by the
OL,13,Fafternoon. Brisk westerly winds across
OL,14,Fthe west. Patchy rain spreading
OL,15,Fsoutheast in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
